<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200901/4b4cf23554fa45cd8776b527d4e29d4c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200901/65f792e289c04a1b928411d8285b30a3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">实在让人不多想不行。</p>
